    <a title="Robert Intriago" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/3076319-robert-intriago"><img alt="Robert Intriago" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1579449867p2/3076319.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
