<span id="freeTextContainer5552414760763385609">Happy thought for the day:<br/><br/>At least I don&apos;t have to include a stint as an analyst for Moody&apos;s or Standard &amp; Poor&apos;s to my list of professional shortcomings. </span>
  <span id="freeText5552414760763385609" style="display:none">Happy thought for the day:<br /><br />At least I don't have to include a stint as an analyst for Moody's or Standard &amp; Poor's to my list of professional shortcomings. </span>
